        "content": "<p>It's just <code>write</code> called in a loop: <a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/src/std/io/mod.rs.html#1446-1461\">https://doc.rust-lang.org/src/std/io/mod.rs.html#1446-1461</a></p>",
